value: SELECT AVG(`Employee Salary`) AS `avg_Employee_Salary_ok`,   `Employee Name` AS `none_Employee_Name_nk` FROM Staples   INNER JOIN (   SELECT COUNT(1) AS `XTableau_join_flag`,     `Call Center Region` AS `none_Call_Center_Region_nk`,     `Employee Name` AS `none_Employee_Name_nk`   FROM Staples   GROUP BY `Call Center Region`,     `Employee Name`   HAVING ((AVG(`Employee Salary`) >= 102499.99999999898) AND (AVG(`Employee Salary`) <= 110000.00000000111)) ) t0 ON ((`Call Center Region` = t0.none_Call_Center_Region_nk) AND (`Employee Name` = t0.none_Employee_Name_nk)) GROUP BY `Employee Name`
